sequenceDiagram
    participant U as Usuario
    participant S as Sentinela
    participant O as IntersectionObserver
    participant G as Gerenciador
    participant DB as IndexedDB

    U->>U: Rola a pagina
    U->>S: Sentinela entra na viewport
    S->>O: isIntersecting true
    O->>G: Callback executado
    G->>DB: getAll com offset e limit 15
    DB-->>G: Proximo lote de tarefas
    G->>G: Renderiza novas tarefas
    G->>S: Move sentinela para o fim
